      • operationNames

        public static Set<String> operationNames()
        In order to minimize the classes needed to bridge between a loaded Func Bundle and the Runner, there are a series of named "operations" that are functions that the Runner can query from the Func Bundle and invoke. It also may be that stuff within the Func Bundle does the same. Thus, we provide a list of named operations.
        Returns:
        the known, named operations
